high_descs: Walk forward to the wall then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the sink that's on your right and stand facing it so you can use it.
Wash the knife in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the counter then turn left.
Open the drawer farthest away from you that's under the counter to your right and put the knife in there before closing it again.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Move forward and turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the knife from the center of the table.
Carry the knife and turn to the right and then face the sink on the right.
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the knife.
Hold the knife and turn around to the counter. Face the left side wall.
Open the top drawer and place the knife inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and place it in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on your right.
Grab a knife from the table.
Go to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the knife in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Walk to the kitchen counter with the coffee maker on it.
Put the knife in the top-left drawer.
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and put it away.
